        <p>At Rogue Reformed Church, we believe grace is not lightweight.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>The Weekly Lift:</strong> Word &amp; Sacrament. No smoke machines. Just Christ clearly proclaimed.</li>
          <li><strong>Doctrine That Carries the Load:</strong> Confessional faith built for suffering, doubt, and long Mondays.</li>
          <li><strong>Spiritual Disciplines (No Shortcuts):</strong> Repentance, prayer, Scripture, generosity, and perseverance.</li>
          <li><strong>Covenant Community:</strong> Spotters included. Accountability, encouragement, and shepherding.</li>
          <li><strong>Endurance for the Long Race:</strong> Faithfulness over decades—families discipled, neighbors loved, churches planted.</li>
        </ul>

